{"tid":1163042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食食吓飯盒，突然有啲想喊。。","createTime":"2019-05-20T08:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:31:10.000Z","uid":195396,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00febd2538fcbf84be45d443fcceb86c08050ad5","tid":1163042,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"以前細個聽到人講捱飯盒捱飯盒<br />\n但嗰陣覺得明明飯盒好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點解叫捱<br />\n中學嗰陣成日要15分鐘啪個飯盒 為咗補課做mock<br />\n但都因為忙 即使食得好狼狽 但都無咩感覺<br />\n加上飯盒唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直都唔覺係捱<br />\n<br />\n而家一個人喺外國讀緊書<br />\n一個人買咗個飯盒坐喺food court<br />\n食食吓有啲想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明唔係難食<br />\n明明唔算cheap<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來一個人食飯可以咁多嘢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac381d25f5df90a4504479e47a0e76e1b343fbc","tid":1163042,"uid":50658,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"慣咗就冇事<br />\n一個人咗幾十年都係咁過"},{"pid":"b6b6217959ea81367f3dfb3525dda2cb2a428199","tid":1163042,"uid":195396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ac381d25f5df90a4504479e47a0e76e1b343fbc","tid":1163042,"uid":50658,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"慣咗就冇事<br />\n一個人咗幾十年都係咁過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"我諗起屋企個老人家。。<br />\n喺香港我同嫲嫲住<br />\n呀爺去得早 交低嫲嫲畀我老豆<br />\n但我兩老又忙 成日唔得閒煮飯<br />\n好多時都係買飯畀嫲嫲一個人食。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好後悔以前無好好陪嫲嫲食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012729218df74abc4cc8